                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-30-defend338 t18240114-30-punish176"></join>
               Transported for Life
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>ROSETTA - <rs id="t18240114-30-verdict177" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240114-30-verdict177" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
